{"tid":2012802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做人應向前看 海洋公園執柒左佢","createTime":"2020-05-12T01:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T02:29:44.000Z","uid":5205,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"307162cf01911957944b737bc0669bf2f1ef1828","tid":2012802,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T01:53:48.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>做人應向前看 海洋公園執柒左佢"},{"pid":"3afe4529c48263b3a58a007f11870bb1c80829ce","tid":2012802,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T01:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />專做支那狗生意，執左都唔可憐"},{"pid":"b3fe8ca6b52d8b848b023a8ae6be7e5ec7fbebe1","tid":2012802,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T01:58:08.000Z","msg":"係港共唔想佢執only"},{"pid":"68b3355cb9680d7074f41148634aab34c3781815","tid":2012802,"uid":229609,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:12:58.000Z","msg":"對海洋公園有情意結......<br />\n我小時候常常進出醫院,而入得最多既就係葛亮洪醫院。<br />\n而海洋公園係位於葛亮洪醫院對面既。13歲時我要做手術住院3個月,因為離家太遠,父母很少來探我,當我卧病在床,望出窗就是海洋公園既海馬標誌同埋d行得好撚慢既纜車......<br />\n我當時諗,對面人人都好開心,而我就要一個人,好痛,好孤獨咁訓係床上面......<br />\n我當時同自己講,我出院之後一定要去對面開開心心咁玩一日!<br />\n海洋公園曾經俾到當時無助既我一絲安慰,所以我真係唔想見到佢步荔園既後塵......<br />\n純粹個人感受,不喜勿插......"},{"pid":"060e0d4a685881e992e49847c3989e82b9026267","tid":2012802,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b3fe8ca6b52d8b848b023a8ae6be7e5ec7fbebe1","tid":2012802,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T01:58:08.000Z","msg":"係港共唔想佢執only"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:21:19.000Z","msg":"留返個海洋公園燒政府錢唔好咩？<br />\n啲錢拎嚟養海豚好過養狗。"},{"pid":"ddbbce73d0afbcfa1a98a9c49c79fa95649578e8","tid":2012802,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:28:52.000Z","msg":"我媽媽過身前,<br />\n佢帶左我去海洋公園過生日,<br />\n海洋公園對我來講,<br />\n係同媽媽最後一次, 最親密嘅回憶,<br />\n我就係靠呢一份回憶, 堅強行到今日<br />\n<br />\n無海洋公園就唔會有今日嘅我"},{"pid":"26ab52dd032cef90ba84f81b8d0d20fe7d4b6849","tid":2012802,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:29:44.000Z","msg":"執柒左佢啦，拎黎起公屋比人蝗蟲住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}